1. *Popodne* je najlepše ugodno vreme za šetnju. (The afternoon is the most pleasant time for a walk.)

2. U *popodnevnim* časovima boravak u parku je sve češći. (In the afternoon hours, staying in the park is becoming more frequent.)

3. *Popodnevna* šetnja imala je neverovatan učinak na njegovo zdravlje. (The afternoon walk had an amazing effect on his health.)

4. *Popodnevne* aktivnosti obično uključuju slobodno vreme. (Afternoon activities usually involve free time.)

5. U *popodnevnim* satima deca igraju igre na ulici. (In the afternoon hours, children play games on the street.)